high_descs: Turn right and move to the desk on your left.
Pick the pan with credit card in it.
Turn around and head to the fridge in the kitchen by slight turns on your right.
Place the pan in the fridge and pick it back after few seconds.
Turn around and head to the cabinet on your left.
Place the pan with credit card in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place the pan with credit card in the cabinet by keeping it in the fridge.

high_descs: Stand up turn around walk towards the desk.
Pick up the pan from the desk.
Turn around walk towards the fridge.
Put the pan into the fridge and pick it back up.
Turn around walk towards the cabinet.
Keep the pan inside the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put the pan into the fridge,take it back and keep it inside the cabinet.
